data.title: Jawaban UAS Morphosyntax
data.meta_description:
Jawaban UAS Morphosyntax - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. 1) KH Ahmad Dahlan is regarded as the founder of modern Islamic education in Indonesia and established the Muhammadiyah organization in 1912. 

2) Muhammadiyah was established to address the backwardness of Indonesian Muslims in areas of life, their poverty, and the condition of traditional Islamic education. 

3) Under KH Ahmad Dahlan and his students, Muhammadiyah pioneered modernization in fields like Islamic education, healthcare, and orphanages and continues to operate schools, universities, and other social programs across Indonesia today.
